<style>
  body {
    background-image: url('../assets/home/background-home-mobile.jpg');
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-size: cover;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    body {
      background-image: url('../assets/home/background-home-tablet.jpg');
    }
  }

  .space {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .space__content {
    padding: 2.5rem 2.4rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .space__content {
      padding: 10rem;
    }
  }

  .space__title,
  .space__heading,
  .space__text {
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .space__heading {
      font-size: 2rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.338rem;
    }
  }

  .space__title {
    line-height: 10rem;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .space__title {
      line-height: 15rem;
      font-size: 15rem;
      padding: 2.5rem;
    }
  }

  .space__text {
    line-height: 2.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .space__text {
      line-height: 2.8rem;
      padding: 0 8rem;
    }
  }

  .space__explore {
    padding: 5.5rem 0;
  }

  .space__link {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;

    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.125rem;
    font-size: 2rem;
    width: 15rem;
    height: 15rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    color: var(--dark-blue);
    background-color: var(--white);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .space__link {
      width: 24.2rem;
      height: 24.2rem;
      font-size: 3.2rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2rem;
    }
  }
</style>

<main class="space">
  <div class="space__content">
    <h5 class="space__heading">So, you want to travel to</h5>
    <h1 class="space__title">Space</h1>
    <p class="space__text">
      Space Let’s face it; if you want to go to space, you might as well
      genuinely go to outer space and not hover kind of on the edge of it. Well
      sit back, and relax because we’ll give you a truly out of this world
      experience!
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="space__explore">
    <a href="/" class="space__link">Explore</a>
  </div>
</main>
